snippet.title: HITMAN - Episode Two: Sapienza Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
HITMAN - Episode Two: Sapienza is available April 26 on PS4, Xbox One and PC. 
The beautiful, sun-drenched coastal town of Sapienza is full of new challenges and packed with opportunities for the creative assassin to explore. Learn more about Sapienza: https://hitman.com/news/sapienza-trailer-release-notes

To buy HITMAN: http://buy.hitman.com
